Package: transitmattr
Title: R Client for the TransitMatters Data Dashboard API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Andrew", "Kouré", email = "akoure@transitmatters.info", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A thin httr2-based wrapper around the TransitMatters Data Dashboard
    API, providing access to MBTA performance metrics including headways, dwell
    times, travel times, ridership, and service data.
